h4. Actor:
Remittance User.

h4. Description:
This is the landing page of *Instrument Purchase* with input form on top and grid view at the bottom.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [ARMS|guide:_ShowARMSPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* "Instrument" sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click *Instrument Purchase* link.
* Show Landing Page of *Instrument Purchase*.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Show for instrument purchase" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Get List of all "Instrument Purchase" from server.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show input form on top to [Search "Instrument Purchase"|guide:].
** Show list of all *Instrument Purchase* in grid view of landing page.


* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

